ound\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></nav><main id=\"main-content\" class=\"flex-grow\"><section class=\"relative h-[40vh] min-h-[300px] flex items-center justify-center bg-brand-dark overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-brand-dark/60 z-10\"></div><img alt=\"Manufacturing Excellence\" fetchPriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover grayscale opacity-50\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2064%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2064%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2064%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2064%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2064%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2064%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2064%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2064%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2064%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"relative z-20 text-center space-y-4 px-4\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\"><span class=\"text-brand-secondary font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm\">Our Facility</span><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white uppercase tracking-tight\">World-Class Manufacturing</h1></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center\"><div class=\"space-y-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-dark\">Built for <span class=\"text-brand-primary\">Scale &amp; Precision.</span></h2><p class=\"text-lg text-brand-muted leading-relaxed\">Our Jodhpur-based manufacturing facility is equipped with the latest garment-making machinery, specialized for high-performance athletic wear. We maintain strict environmental and safety standards to ensure a sustainable production environment.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-4\"><div class=\"p-4 bg-brand-surface rounded-brand border border-gray-100\"><h4 class=\"font-bold text-brand-dark\">Modern Machinery</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-brand-muted\">Automated cutting and high-speed stitching machines.</p></div><div class=\"p-4 bg-brand-surface rounded-brand border border-gray-100\"><h4 class=\"font-bold text-brand-dark\">Skilled Workforce</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-brand-muted\">Experienced craftsmen with decades of expertise.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] rounded-brand-lg overflow-hidden relative shadow-card\"><img alt=\"Factory Floor\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1565034946487-077786996e27%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1565034946487-077786996e27%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1565034946487-077786996e27%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1565034946487-077786996e27%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1565034946487-077786996e27%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1565034946487-077786996e27%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1565034946487-077786996e27%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1565034946487-077786996e27%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1565034946487-077786996e27%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"aspect-[3/4] rounded-brand-lg overflow-hidden relative shadow-card mt-8\"><img alt=\"Stitching Unit\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1555529669-26f9d103abdd%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1555529669-26f9d103abdd%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1555529669-26f9d103abdd%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1555529669-26f9d103abdd%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1555529669-26f9d103abdd%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1555529669-26f9d103abdd%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1555529669-26f9d103abdd%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1555529669-26f9d103abdd%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1555529669-26f9d103abdd%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D2070%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 bg-brand-surface\"><div class=\"max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center\"><div class=\"mb-16 space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-brand-dark\">How We Work</h2><p class=\"text-lg text-brand-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Our streamlined manufacturing process ensures consistency, quality, and speed.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"p-8 bg-white rounded-brand-lg border border-gray-100 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all text-left space-y-4 flex flex-col items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark\">1<!-- -->. <!-- -->Analysis</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed\">Detailed requirement gathering and design finalization.</p></div><div class=\"p-8 bg-white rounded-brand-lg border border-gray-100 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all text-left space-y-4 flex flex-col items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-scissors w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"3\"></circle><path d=\"M8.12 8.12 12 12\"></path><path d=\"M20 4 8.12 15.88\"></path><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"18\" r=\"3\"></circle><path d=\"M14.8 14.8 20 20\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark\">2<!-- -->. <!-- -->Cutting</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed\">Precision fabric cutting using advanced machinery.</p></div><div class=\"p-8 bg-white rounded-brand-lg border border-gray-100 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all text-left space-y-4 flex flex-col items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-activity w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark\">3<!-- -->. <!-- -->Stitching</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed\">Expert craftsmanship joined with high-strength threads.</p></div><div class=\"p-8 bg-white rounded-brand-lg border border-gray-100 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all text-left space-y-4 flex flex-col items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clipboard-check w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"8\" height=\"4\" x=\"8\" y=\"2\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><path d=\"m9 14 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark\">4<!-- -->. <!-- -->QC Check</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed\">Multi-layer quality inspections for every unit.</p></div><div class=\"p-8 bg-white rounded-brand-lg border border-gray-100 shadow-card hover:shadow-card-hover transition-all text-left space-y-4 flex flex-col items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0